export default async(e,t={})=>{const c=document.createElement("a");c.download=t.fileName||"Untitled",c.rel="noopener",c.href=URL.createObjectURL(e),c.addEventListener("click",e=>{c.remove(),setTimeout(()=>URL.revokeObjectURL(c.href),3e4)}),setTimeout(()=>c.click(),0)};
